jobPosts.jobDescription: Based in Vancouver, BC and reporting to the Director, Tax & Treasury, the Senior Tax Analyst will be responsible for a variety of Canadian and International corporate income and excise tax matters. The primary role is to support Aurora’s tax compliance and IFRS tax accounting reporting requirements.
